libflex (1.0.2-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Voice-band FSK tones (1200/2400 Hz) for radio compatibility
  * Fixed baseband generator timing drift (float boundaries)
  * RTL-SDR receiver (flex_sdr) with async IQ reader
  * Adaptive squelch for persistent-carrier repeaters
  * Frame-synchronized TX scheduler with flex now bypass
  * 500ms silence lead-in for receiver squelch
  * 131 tests, zero allocation

